dct_title_s: Sarnia Insula, vulgo Garnsey, et Insula Cæsarea, vernacule Iarsey [front]
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Shows boundaries, rivers, woods and settlements ; sea decorated with ships. German text on verso with caption title: Iarsey und Garnsey; p. 483-484; signature Mmmmmmm. From: Novus Atlas, das ist, Welt-beschreibung ... durch Wilhelm und Joan Blaeu. Amsterdami : Apud Johannem Blaeu, 1645-1648. "The German atlas of England has only one edition, with variants in the letterpress title and engraved date."--Koeman, C. Atlantes neerlandici (New ed.), p. 258.
